{"tid":1230194,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"推！保良局中學考試卷公然保「送中」","createTime":"2019-06-16T06:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T17:57:27.000Z","uid":249988,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6c879bbc8a6feb099b915ea742d245cc8641441e","tid":1230194,"uid":249988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:39:25.000Z","msg":"【<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保良局第一張永慶中學</strong></span>學生被迫默寫保「送中」字句  校友聯署聲討】<br />\n六月十三日，在教協呼籲及部分在校學生表明罷課意願後，保一堅持不罷課，亦不設補考予罷課學生。同日，竟有老師以支持逃犯條例的社論為中五英文默書考試材料，選材立場偏頗，內容包括指<span style=\"color: red;\">「香港市民信任特首及送中條例」</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">「所有良好守法的市民都會支持合理的逃犯條例」</span>（見文末）。不少學生，包括較早前爭取罷課不果的學弟妹，為保考試成績，被迫默寫下違心言論。此情此景，不僅嚴重侵反言論自由，更幾乎與勞改無異，令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n有關默寫內容: <br />\n<br />\n&bull; &lsquo;People in Hong Kong have not lost their trust in the chief executive and her stance on the bill. &rsquo;<br />\n&bull; &lsquo;All decent and law-abiding citizens would support a proper extradition law to deter and weed out offenders hiding in the city.&rsquo;<br />\n&bull; &lsquo;Hong Kong will be a much better place to live in and its reputation as &ldquo;Asia&rsquo;s world city&rdquo; will be greatly enhanced if the government takes serious and substantive steps to enact legislation to uphold justice and clear its name as a &ldquo;haven for fugitives&rdquo;.&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n全文見link<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd2foDWZs307-GbQe6W8vgEXmaXN-HFqnrNINNh9k98_jdmgQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSd2foDWZs307-GbQe6W8vgEXmaXN-HFqnrNINNh9k98_jdmgQ%2Fviewform&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=97e66749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd2foDWZs307-GbQe6W8vgEXmaXN-HFqnrNINNh9k98_jdmgQ/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"a60cdca0d18079643fb3dd20b0fc82f75deaabf3","tid":1230194,"uid":229955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:40:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大會宣布 提前出發 @ 14:30 <br />\n<br />\n1) 由維園 去 金鐘添美道<br />\n2) 2 條 BANNER : 「痛心疾首」 「撤回惡法」 由宗教界 同 一班媽媽帶領<br />\n3) 「痛心疾首」 BANNER 會放喺適當地方 , 畀各市民獻花<br />\n4) 有宗教界負責安排 祈禱會<br />\n5) 有支援抗爭者基金籌款箱<br />\n<br />\n616 黑色大遊行 五大宗旨:<br />\n<br />\n1) 撒回惡法<br />\n2) 釋放被捕既抗爭者<br />\n3) 我們不是暴徒<br />\n4) 追究黑警開槍責任<br />\n5) 淋病下台</span></span>"},{"pid":"af7c4d87f7bc02c7c682847eb8049f39fc34f9f4","tid":1230194,"uid":249988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:04:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c04b0268092db3373a5526cb74890101cbe8f76a","tid":1230194,"uid":249988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:04:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cd4f5e0435f8eba2301a3895c7f646e6aeb761e2","tid":1230194,"uid":249988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:04:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5300f9655050a1a7ca0a542a72f144943657df3b","tid":1230194,"uid":249988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0eb7c31d5b6b1e7c4579c3593eb0158d64420f27","tid":1230194,"uid":249988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:12:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ddced7879a0927dd9df1a5d22897cf8fd04c0f47","tid":1230194,"uid":137725,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"發現大多數仆街教畜都係5 60後，呢單都應該好難唔係"},{"pid":"36025ed95ac9b8911d14f6ccf86e258e30cacf00","tid":1230194,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:28:22.000Z","msg":"入面係咪全部新香港人讀"},{"pid":"6f24a21cb4ed94f3d3808f86efa52b0aff7eb2a1","tid":1230194,"uid":236222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:11:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d521481712f185988a3b37f134ddecde585d9357","tid":1230194,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:00:06.000Z","msg":